Package: montyhall
Title: Monty Hall Game Simulator
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Functions to simulate the classic Monty Hall problem (three doors, one car, two goats). Includes helpers to create a game, select and change doors, determine winners, and run many simulations to compare the 'stay' vs 'switch' strategies.
